1.1.1.name: wordpress/my-videotag
1.1.1.description:
ENGLISH

This Plugin will add a Tag called "video", which automatically identifies videos from sites like: youtube.com, Youtube.com Playlist, dailymotion.com, metacafe.com, myspace, yahoo, megavideo.com, vimeo.com, gamevideos.com, tu.tv, godtube.com, myvideo.com, collegehumor.com, comedycentral.com, revver.com, clipfish.com, aniboom.com, current.com, facebook.com, funnyordie.com, dotsub.com, dorkly.com, scribd.com, justin.tv, citytv.com.co, snotr.com, videobb.com, videozer.com, novamov.com, youku.com, vxv.com, clipshack.com and add them to your post or comments Wordpress.
